Package: trelloR
Title: R API for Trello
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jakub", "Chromec", , "chromec.jakub@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Irina", "Matusevich", role = "crr")
    )
Description: Provides access to Trello API. A family of GET functions make it
    easy to retrieve cards, labels, members, teams and other data from both
    public and private boards. Server responses are formatted upon retrieval.
    Automated paging allows for large requests that exceed server limit.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.3)
Imports:
    dplyr (>= 0.5),
    httr (>= 1.2),
    jsonlite (>= 1.0)
License: GPL-3
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
